army

Class Army

  • java.lang.Object
    • army.Army

  • public class Army
extends java.lang.Object
    The Army class stores all the objects and shows which side they belong to(either the Forces of Darkness or the Forces of Light). It populates the various armies and also enables the user to edit the values of the fields in the various armies.
    Version:
    Lab Assignment 3: The Hobbit Battlefield Simulator
    Author:
    Elim Yao Tsiagbey and Rex Woollard
